review_blob: I like it. Good Tasmanian beer, fresh, lively, almost like boags, beauty. Can taste the Tassie hops.
Fucking shocking beer. leaves a taste like grass and bark in your mouth. avoid at all costs. Pretty colour, shit taste.
First imported beer i ever tasted. Not bad, but bland. Not much nose, but finishes nicely. Similar to Tooheys Blue.
Better rating beer, good strong, firm upper palate, lingers a nutty flavour... quite enjoyable. Best asain beer around.
Not the nicest Aussie beers, goes well with BBQd seafood, easy to drink, lacks punch in the after mouth. Quite refreshing
